00:24:57,492 --> 00:25:00,053
So it's a pretty frustrating that we're paying for that.

279
00:25:00,433 --> 00:25:02,174
So, uh, just a little bit of money.

280
00:25:02,334 --> 00:25:08,418
So if the city's paying some percentage of that, uh, you know, just looking to the resident to have a little skin in the game, make sure that, you know,

281
00:25:08,814 --> 00:25:15,157
that they get the product out on the street in time for pickup and go from there and see how that takes.

282
00:25:15,577 --> 00:25:17,277
Is that number going up?

283
00:25:17,938 --> 00:25:21,219
If you take the number, it's about 615 bulk items every two weeks.

284
00:25:21,639 --> 00:25:23,260
That's a lot.

285
00:25:23,280 --> 00:25:24,560
Like I said, I think we're at like 17,000.

286
00:25:24,920 --> 00:25:26,441
Yeah, I did 400,000 divided by 20.

287
00:25:26,681 --> 00:25:28,942
Yeah, I mean, maybe you can look at maybe less of that.

288
00:25:29,702 --> 00:25:33,684
Have you noticed an increase in the bulk items?

289
