I think there's different levels of rubbish, but that's, I think, once you remove that compostable items and those go in the 13-gallon bin,

295
00:26:10,974 --> 00:26:18,496
The idea is that the 64-gallon bin will be enough for the two weeks.

296
00:26:19,637 --> 00:26:23,198
But, you know, if there's overflow situations, we're going to have accommodations for that as well.

297
00:26:23,458 --> 00:26:25,458
So we'll continue, still continue buying the bags?

298
00:26:25,738 --> 00:26:26,799
Buying bags, yeah.

299
00:26:26,819 --> 00:26:35,981
And we're going to look at what the haulers propose, too, because we brainstormed what's feasible, but we're letting the haulers tell us what will work for them.

