00:29:25,796 --> 00:29:31,299
They have been hoping for a while that they could, quote, piggyback on our waste contract.

336
00:29:31,379 --> 00:29:35,540
It's something we actually spoke with Jeffrey Driscoll, the executive director, last week about it.

