339
00:29:53,193 --> 00:29:54,314
We don't we would like to stop it.

340
00:29:55,035 --> 00:29:56,156
I mean, can.

341
00:29:57,157 --> 00:30:00,200
How do we, what is the plan, so the business district.

342
00:30:00,781 --> 00:30:11,472
Yeah, so one of those solutions that we're exploring and heading in the direction of is working with businesses with limited space especially in the business districts for container disposal.

343
00:30:13,033 --> 00:30:18,579
Sounds great, but it's a very challenging thing just thinking about it, which put the container.

344
00:30:18,619 --> 00:30:23,164
Yep, ready for the container the city would have to help, I think, with some of the potentially our public space.

345
00:30:24,084 --> 00:30:26,127
So there's some work to do there for sure.

346
00:30:26,247 --> 00:30:33,994
So because what we don't want to continue is black trash bags in our squares once a week, is, is the option of.

