00:30:35,545 --> 00:30:40,467
picking them up in the evening, like some cities do.

348
00:30:40,707 --> 00:30:41,487
Not gonna rule it out.

349
00:30:41,787 --> 00:30:41,948
Huh?

350
00:30:42,148 --> 00:30:42,848
Not gonna rule it out.

351
00:30:43,328 --> 00:30:46,629
No, I guess, hey, let them put it out and then they'll come by like at midnight.

