00:33:36,965 --> 00:33:50,337
How much are we spending right now on- I don't know off the top of my head, as far as hauling the- Well, yeah, I mean, with the advent of Amazon, you buy something this big and they send you a box that big.

392
00:33:50,637 --> 00:33:50,957
Sure, sure.

393
00:33:53,728 --> 00:34:02,193
Have we seen an increase in how many times they're emptying that out over the last few years with all these home deliveries?

